<h1>The Heart: The Engine of Life</h1>
<h2>A Human Heart Tutorial</h2>
<h3>Program Guide</h3>
<p>
<a href="/ftp/p11_ftps.htm"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10 SRC="/pics/icons/ftp_dl4.gif" ALT="FTP Downloadable Software!">Downloadable software!</a>
<p>
This is a guide for an interactive shareware educational program
called THE HEART: THE ENGINE OF LIFE.  It contains numerous wonderful
educational animations and runs on virtually any IBM-PC compatible
computer!  Best of all, it can be downloaded <b>in it's entirety</b> 
from our web site and other shareware distributors! It is a shareware 
program and a registration fee of just $25.00 is requested if you use 
the program!  Before being released as shareware, this program had 
been sold to thousands of hospitals, schools, doctors offices, and 
individuals.  Please download the program and enjoy learning about
your most amazing and wonderful organ--your heart!
<p>
