<title> Russell D. Hoffman Interviews Chip Designer Carolyn Spivak </title>
</header>
<META Name="description" Content="Russell D. Hoffman interviews Chip Designer Carolyn Spivak">
<META Name="keywords" Content="interview design what does a chip designer do?">
<body>
