<a href="/complain/complain.htm"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=20 SRC="/pics/icons/complain.gif" ALT=""></A>
<b>From</b> <a href="/complain/complain.htm"><i>EXAMPLES IN THE ART OF COMPLAINING</i></a> by Russell D. Hoffman
