<hr>
<h1> Pre-Computer art by Russell D. Hoffman</h1>
<hr>
<a href="/pics/icons/ascologo.gif"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10 WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=14 SRC="/pics/icons/ascolog1.gif" ALT=""></a>
<p>
There are definitely some similarities between these images and some
of the <a href="randomar.htm">random computerized art</a> also exhibited at this web 
site.  I drew these images mainly in the late 1970's.  I have scanned them
in at relatively low resolution for presentation here.  There are
high-resolution TIFF images of these available, each about 4
megabytes in size, except one (template.tif) which is 25 megabytes. 
(Please contact us if you would like to purchase a large format image.)
<p>
<a href="allyoung.htm">Click here to download all the high-resolution
images in one step (go get a cup of coffee--it's a little over 450K)</a>
<hr>
<p>
<a href="/pics/random/youngart/blueci08.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=154 HEIGHT=97 HSPACE=4 SRC="/pics/random/youngart/blueci10.jpg" ALT="Blue Circle Image"></a>
<p>
<h5>Blue Background with Circles</h5>  (66K GIF)  Rapidograph and Dr. Martins Inks.  Blue created with tissue paper brush.
<p>
<br>
<a href="/pics/random/youngart/blueli08.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=195 HEIGHT=131 HSPACE=4 SRC="/pics/random/youngart/blueli11.gif" ALT="Blue Lines Image"></a>
<p>
<h5>Blue Lines Towards a sun</h5>  (19K GIF)  Rapidograph and Dr. Martins Inks.
<p>
<br>
<a href="/pics/random/youngart/explod40.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=207 HEIGHT=152 HSPACE=4 SRC="/pics/random/youngart/explod35.gif" ALT="Explosion Image"></a>
<p>
<h5>Explosion</h5>  (124K GIF) Rapidograph and Dr. Martins Inks.
<p>
<br>
<a href="/pics/random/youngart/zigzag06.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=289 HEIGHT=203 HSPACE=4 SRC="/pics/random/youngart/zigza05s.gif" ALT="Zig Zag Image"></a>
<p>
<h5>Zig Zags</h5>  (39K GIF)  Rapidograph and Dr. Martins Inks.
<p>
<br>
<a href="/pics/random/youngart/frnchc09.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=331 HEIGHT=197 HSPACE=4 SRC="/pics/random/youngart/frnch09s.gif" ALT="French Curve Image"></a>
<p>
<h5>French Curve</h5>  (30K GIF)  Rapidograph and Dr. Martins Inks, French Curve.
<p>
