<a href="/pics/random/youngart/squigg08.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH=282 HEIGHT=203 HSPACE=4 SRC="/pics/random/youngart/squig05s.gif" ALT="Squiggles Image"></a>
