http://www.animatedsoftware.com:80/spacedeb/junk9602.htm 205.216.158.236 19970222093822 text/html 10498
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Communications/1.1
Date: Saturday, 22-Feb-97 09:40:55 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 03-Feb-97 20:25:12 GMT
Content-length: 10307
