<h1> Computer Drawings by Dr. Howard S. Hoffman </h1>
<hr>
<a href="/pics/icons/ascologo.gif"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10 WIDTH=32 HEIGHT=14 SRC="/pics/icons/ascolog1.gif" ALT=""></a>
<p>
Listing of available drawings from "the ol' professor".  All are in 256 color GIF format, and
are too big for most browsers at this time, but can be scrolled. 
They were created using Microsoft Paint on a Pentium computer in Spring, 1996. 
<p>
<hr>
<ul><b>List of available drawings</b>
