<li>   <a href="/family/howardsh/wisdom.gif">(59K) Wisdom consists of knowing when to avoid perfection</a>
<li>   <a href="/family/howardsh/sunday.gif">(60K) I thought it was Sunday</a>
</ul>
<hr>
<p>
<b>Artwork by Dr. Howard S. Hoffman, Professor Emeritus of Psychology at
Bryn Mawr College, Bryn Mawr, PA.</b>
<p>
Presented online by his son Russell who eggs him into doing these things.
