<a name="top"> </a>
<a href="/pics/geni/genimcga/genimcga.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM HSPACE=20 SRC="/pics/geni/genimcga/genimcga.gif" ALT="Global Energy Network International"></a>
<hr>
<h3> What Can I Do? </h3>
<a href="/pics/geni/genimcga/dymaunfl.gif"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=20 SRC="/pics/geni/genimcga/dymaunfl.gif" ALT="Unfolded Dymaxion Globe"></a>
<p>
Your help is needed to improve the quality of life for everyone without damage to the planet - to make this vision a reality.
<p>
<hr>
<p>
   1)  Request the GENI Information Document ($US15) or one of our videos ($US20 ea.)
<p>
   2)  Contact the media and your political leaders.  Give them a copy of this program.
<p>
   3)  Contribute money or skills to further the research and education about this global solution.  Contributions to GENI are tax-deductible in the U.S.
<p>
<hr>
