<head>
<title>Sandhills.Net: What's New</title>
</head>
<body background="./graphics/n_r_grn.gif">
<h2>What's New at Sandhills.Net</h2>
Welcome to Sandhills.Net.  This site is brought to you by 
<a href="./sandlink.html"> SandLink</a> in
cooperation with the Sandhills Area Chamber of Commerce and several locally based organizations.  This site began as a community project and it is our sincerest desire that it contin
ue in that fashion.  If you have ideas, talent, energy or skills that you would like to contribute <a href="mailto:sacc@ac.net">please let us know</a>.
<br><br>
Thanks for stopping by!
<hr>
<b>970128</b>
The <a href="http://www.sandhills.net/inf.html"><b>Visitor's Information</b></a> page has been updated with calendars of events for the first 6 months of 1997.
Wouldn't this be a good time to take a minute to see what's going on in our community?<br><br>

<hr>
<b>970103</b>
We have new supporters!<br><br>
<a href="http://www.manorcare.com"><b>Manor Care Nursing Center</b></a><br>
<a href="http://pinehurstbrewery.com"><b>Pinehurst Village Brewery</b></a><br>
<a href="http://www.travelresorts.com"><b>Travel Resorts of America</b></a><br><br>
When you support these businesses please also support Sandhills.Net by mentioning that you saw their links on our pages.  THANK!

<hr>
<b>961028</b>
We have a <a href="http://www.sandhills.net/gb/guestbook.html">guest book</a> on the <a
href="http://www.sandhills.net/inf.html"><b>Visitors Information</b></a> page now.  Please take a
moment and sign in.  Thanks!
<hr>
<b>960926</b><br>
<a href="http://www.sjp.org"><b>St. Joseph of the Pines</b></a> now has a full suite of pages at their own site.  You can access them though the health link.  Their name is hot-linked as a page sponsor.  Stop by soon and find out more about this major community member!
<hr>
<b>960726</b><br>
Check out the new restaurant guide, local weather links, calendar of events and local map links on the <a href="http://www.sandhills.net/inf.html"><b>Visitor Information</b></a> page.<br><br>

Also, look at our new <a href="http://www.sandhills.net/communit.html"><b>Comm-Unity</b></a> page.  Sandhills.Net is THE community based website for the Sandhills of Moore County, North Carolina.  This page is being built to provide links to other area pages.
<hr>
<b>960717</b><br>
We've given our front page a face-lift.  This includes the new business card size promotional.  These images rotate on a random basis.  There will be a limited number in the rotation.  <a href="mailto:webmaster@sandhills.net">Let us know</a> if you would like prices to have your logo included in this limited rotation.
<hr>
<b>960629</b><br>
We've added some description on the search page and hopefully made it easier to understand how to use it.  If anyone has and questions or suggestions we would love to hear from you.
<hr>
<b>960623</b><br>
Local residents and visitors alike will find it easier to locate specific services and businesses with the new search feature in the <a href="./bizclass.html">Business</a> link on<A HREF="./san.html"> The Chamber</A> page.<br>
<hr>
