<H3 ALIGN=CENTER><FONT COLOR="#FF0000"><FONT SIZE=+3>G</FONT></FONT><FONT COLOR="#0000FF">overnment
in the</FONT> <FONT COLOR="#FF0000"><FONT SIZE=+3>S</FONT></FONT><FONT COLOR="#0000FF">andhills</FONT></H3>

<P>
<HR WIDTH="100%"></P>

<P><IMG SRC="./graphics/rwb.gif" ALT="banner" HEIGHT=48 WIDTH=192 ALIGN=RIGHT></P>

<P><A HREF="http://www.mindspring.com/~vandy/"><IMG SRC="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" ALT="*" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=9 WIDTH=9 ALIGN=BOTTOM></A><A HREF="http://www.mindspring.com/~vandy/">
County of Moore WWW Site</A></P>

<P><A HREF="http://www.sandhills.net/state.html"><IMG SRC="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" ALT="*" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=9 WIDTH=9 ALIGN=BOTTOM></A><A HREF="http://www.sandhills.net/state.html">
North Carolina State Government</A></P>

<P><A HREF="http://www.sandhills.net/federal.html"><IMG SRC="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" ALT="*" BORDER=0 HEIGHT=9 WIDTH=9 ALIGN=BOTTOM></A><A HREF="http://www.sandhills.net/federal.html">
Federal Government</A><BR>
</P>

<P>
<HR></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+3>T</FONT>his site contains a wide variety of government
resources that should be of interest to citizens of the Sandhills area
of North Carolina. We hope that you find the information here to be helpful
and stimulating. For instance . . . </P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+3>A</FONT>re you registered to vote in Moore County? You
can find out how from the <A HREF="http://www.mindspring.com/~vandy/elec.htm">Moore
County Board of Elections</A>. Are you ready for spring planting? Check
with the <A HREF="http://www.mindspring.com/~vandy/coext.htm">Moore County
Cooperative Extension Service</A> for the latest information. </P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+3>W</FONT>e also provide you access to the <A HREF="http://www.whitehouse.gov/">Whitehouse</A>,
the <A HREF="http://www.senate.gov/">U.S. Senate</A> and the <A HREF="http://www.house.gov/">U.S.
House of Representatives</A>.<BR>
</P>

<P>
<HR></P>

<P>Our <B>Government</B> page is sponsored by the <B><I><A HREF="http://www.mindspring.com/~vandy/">County
of Moore.</A></I></B> </P>

<P>For more information about this site, or to suggest additional materials,
please <B><A HREF="mailto:info@sandhills.net">send us e-mail.</A></B></P>

