<head>
<title>Moore Regional Hospital</title>
</head>

<body background="./graphics/m0oe9ihe.gif">

<h3>Moore Regional Hospital</h3>
<hr>
<img align=left alt="MRH" src="./graphics/mrh2.jpg">

<p>Moore Regional Hospital, which was recently named one of the top 100 hospitals in the United States, is a 400-bed, acute care, not-for-profit hospital which serves as the referral center for a 14-county region in the 
Carolinas. With an active Medical Staff of 140 physicians, a professional staff of more than 2,000 and more than 500 volunteers, the hospital has many sophisticated medical capabilities usually found only in much larger metropolitan areas. Moore Regional also serves as the flagship hospital for 
FirstHealth of the Carolinas, the region's only comprehensive healthcare system.
<hr>
<img align=right alt="H&FC" src="./graphics/h_fc2.jpg">
<p>The Moore Regional Health & Fitness Center offers the most comprehensive and varied array of wellness and fitness programs in the Sandhills. A division of Moore Regional Hospital, members receive a health assessment that includes a computerized wellness profile, cardiovascular evaluation and body composition analysis. The center also offers an eight-lane indoor pool, strength training equipment, racquetball courts, aerobics studios, sauna/steam room, basketball/volleyball court, indoor cushioned walking/jogging track and child care service.

<p>For more information about services offered at either the hospital or the fitness center, please call (910) 215-1478.

<hr>
<center>
<a href="./hea.html"><img src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt=" * " border=0 height=9 width=9 align=bottom>Sandhills.Net: Health</a>
</center>


</body>
