<center><H2>November 1996</h2></center>
<HR>
<pre>

  November 1 -   LAWN BOWLING.  Visitors welcome to participate in lawn
  December 31    bowling at the weekly club bowling days, Mondays,
                 Wednesdays and Saturdays.  Pinehurst Flag Circle
                 Green, Pinehurst Resort & Country Club.  For more
                 information call (910) 295-6689.

  1              DECORATIVE ART SHOW (JURIED).  Opening exhibit at
                 Campbell House, Connecticut Avenue, Southern Pines. 
                 For more information call (910) 692-4356.

  1 - 3          CATAWBA CLASSIC FIELD TRIAL.  Hours:  8 AM to late
                 afternoon.  Sandhills Wildlife Area, Hoffman, NC.  For
                 more information call (704)596-6816.

