                 Rockingham Dragway, Rockingham.  For more information
                 call (910) 582-3400.

  4              MID CAROLINAS GOLF TOURNAMENT.  Shotgun start.  Hours:
                 11:30 AM.  Woodlake Country Club, Vass.  For more
                 information call (910) 245-4686 or (910) 245-4031.

  4              CLASSICAL CONCERT SERIES.  "Tower Brass Quintet", a
                 world top brass delight.  Hours:  8 PM.  Performing
                 Arts Center, Southern Pines.  For more information
                 call (910) 692-6273 or (910) 692-4356.

  6 - 10         TAR HEEL OPEN ALL AGE CHAMPIONSHIP FIELD TRIALS.  
                 Hours:  8 AM to late afternoon.  Sandhills
                 Wildlife Area, Hoffman, NC.  For more information call
                 (704)596-6816.

  7 - 10         HOMER CUMMINGS GOLF TOURNAMENT.  Mid Pines Inn & Golf
                 Club.  For more information call (910) 692-2114.

  9              GOLF CHORUS EXTRAVAGANZA.  Barbershop quartet music.  
