                 Lee Auditorium, off Hwy. 15/501.  For more information
                 call Brud Everette at (910) 295-2197.

  9              PET PARADE & BARK-IN-THE-PARK FESTIVAL.  Sponsored by
                 the Humane Society of Moore County.  Hours:  9 AM -
                 until;  park by Pennsylvania Ave., downtown Southern
                 Pines.  For more information call (910) 692-6476.

  9 - 10         GO-CART EVENT.  Go-Cart Racing. NC Motor Speedway,
                 Rockingham.  For more information call (704)764-7418
                 or (910) 582-2861.

  10             MOORE COUNTY CONCERT BAND PERFORMANCE.  Hours:  2 PM. 
                 A complimentary concert held in the Pinehurst Hotel,
                 Cardinal Ballroom.  For more information call
                 (910) 295-8415.

  11 - 17        CENTRAL CAROLINA FIELD TRIAL CLUB - BIRD DOG TRIALS.  
                 Dogs handled from horseback.  Spectators welcome, no
                 charge.  Rental horses available.  Hours:  8 AM - 5
                 PM.  Sandhills Wildlife Management Area, Hoffman, NC. 
