                 Auditorium.  For more information call (910) 692-4356.

  15 - 16        JAZZ BAND CONCERT,  "Up a Lazy River".  Hours:  8 PM. 
                 Owens Auditorium, Sandhills Community College,
                 Pinehurst. Admission charge.  For more information
                 call (910) 695-3829 or (910) 692-6185.

  16 - 17        PUFFINS OF THE ROCKY COAST.  An event celebrating
                 puffins and other sea birds, with special programming
                 in the Rocky Coast exhibit area of the North American
                 Region and special entertainment in the North American
                 Plaza.  NC Zoological Park, Asheboro.  For more
                 information call (800)488-0444.

  23 - 24        SANDHILLS CENTRAL MODEL RAILROAD CLUB OPEN HOUSE.  
