                 Level Campbell House, Southern Pines.  For more
                 information call (910) 949-3351.

  24             CHRISTMAS OPEN HOUSE IN CAMERON.  Visit the many
                 antique shops and view the specialty displays.  Hours:
                 1 PM - 5 PM.  Cameron.  For more information call
                 (910) 245-7042.

