                 information call (910) 692-8161.

  27             NC SYMPHONY HOLIDAY POPS CONCERT.  Hours:  8 PM. 
                 Pinehurst Hotel, Grand Ballroom.  For ticket
                 information call (910) 295-8415.

  November 27 -  THANKSGIVING "TURKEY TOURNAMENT".  Pine Needles Golf
  December 1     Club, Southern Pines.  For information and
                 reservations call (910) 692-7111.

