                  Hours:  2 PM & 8 PM.  Performing Arts Center, Southern
                  Pines.  For more information call (910) 692-4356.

   6 - 8          SANDHILLS LITTLE THEATRE PRESENTS "ALONE TOGETHER",  a
                  comedy by Lawrence Roman.  Delightfully wise and witty
                  comedy of a middle-aged couple whose children have
                  left the nest (or have they???).  Hours:  8 PM.  Owens
                  Auditorium, Sandhills Community College.  For more
                  information call (910) 692-3799.

   8              MOORE COUNTY ARTS SATURDAYS: "THE BAKER, THE BEAR, AND
                  THE BLACKSMITH"  by theatre at Lime Kiln. Hours: 11
                  AM, Performing Arts Center,  Southern Pines;  3 PM
                  Highfalls Elementary School.  For more information
                  call (910) 692-4356.

   8 - 9          "ORCHIDS AT WEYMOUTH."  Exhibits by orchid societies
                  from North and South Carolina, with more than 600
                  plants on display and for sale.  Admission at door.  
                  Hours:  TBD.  Weymouth Center, Southern Pines.  For
                  more information call (910) 692-6261.

   9 - 13         PEGGY KIRK BELL/PINE NEEDLES LADIES "GOLFARI",  Pine
                  Needles Lodge and Golf Club, Southern Pines.  For more
                  information call (910) 692-7111 or (800) 747-7272.

   10             CLASSICAL CONCERT SERIES.  Featuring Gail Niwa, piano;
                  the only female winner of the Gina Bachaver
                  International Piano Competition.  Hours:  8 PM. 
                  Performing Arts Center, Southern Pines.  For more
                  information call (910) 692-6273 or (910) 692-4356.

