                  47th consecutive tour. Admission - $15/ticket.  Hours:
                  10 AM - 5 PM.  Begins at Campbell House, Southern
                  Pines.  For more information call (910) 295-2636 or
                  (910) 692-2106.

   10 - 13        SANDHILLS LITTLE THEATRE PRESENTS "TO KILL A
                  MOCKINGBIRD",  a drama based on the novel by Harper
                  Lee.  Dramatized by Christopher Servel.  A young
                  girl's experiences living in a quiet southern town
                  filled with sensitivity, hostility, defeat and
                  triumph.  Hours:  Thursday - Saturday; 8 PM; Sunday;
                  2:30 PM.  Owens Auditorium, Sandhills Community
                  College.  For more information call (910) 692-3799.

   10 - 13        NC CLUB TEAM DOUBLES CROQUET TOURNAMENT.  Hours:  9 AM
