<font color=green size=+3>1997</font><br>
<h1><font color=green>May in the Sandhills</font></h2>
</center>

<pre>                                    
   1 - 18         FAIR TIME AT FT. BRAGG.  For more information call
                  (910) 396-1024 or (910) 396-6319.

   1 - 31         POLO GAMES  held at Pinehurst Track, Route 5,
                  Pinehurst.  Hours:  2 PM on occasional Sundays.  Call
