                  take their treasures to the streets for a whole day of
                  "antiquing": good food and good fun.  Hours:  10 AM to
                  dark. Free.  Historic District of Cameron.  For more
                  information call (910) 692-7001 or (910) 245-3697.

   4              PINECREST HIGH SCHOOL SPRING BAND CONCERT.  Hours:  2
                  PM.  Robert E. Lee Auditorium, Pinecrest High School. 
