                  the Tyson & Jones Buggy Factory that operated in the
                  1800's and early 1900's. Buggies will be on display,
                  there will be a street dance, craft fair, rodeo, and a
                  wide variety of concessions and entertainment.  Hours:
                  Friday; 7 PM - 11 PM; Saturday; 9 AM - 11 PM. 
