                  (910) 947-2504.

   10             FT. BRAGG HORSE TRIALS.  Novice and training levels of
                  competition, dressage, cross-country and stadium
                  jumping.  Hours:  8 AM - 4 PM.  For more information
                  call (910) 396-5620 or (910) 396-1024.

   10 - 11        PINEHURST HORSE CLASSIC HUNTER JUMPER SHOW.  Open to
                  spectators, food and drinks available.  Hours:  8 AM -
                  4:30 PM.  Pinehurst Harness Track.  For more
                  information call (813) 831-4986 or (910) 295-4446.

   11 - 15        PEGGY KIRK BELL/PINE NEEDLES LADIES "GOLFARI",  Pine
                  Needles Lodge and Golf Club, Southern Pines.  For more
                  information call (910) 692-7111 or (800) 747-7272.

   13             PINECREST HIGH SCHOOL SPRING CHORAL CONCERT.  Hours: 
                  7 PM.  Robert E. Lee Auditorium, Pinecrest High
                  School.  For more information call (910) 692-6554.

   14 - 17        THE ELKS NATIONAL GOLF TOURNAMENT.  Players from all
                  over the country compete on several area courses.  For
