   16 - 18        PINEHURST, CHARLOTTESVILLE AND GREENBRIER INVITATIONAL
                  CROQUET TOURNAMENT.  Hours:  9 AM to 5 PM.  Pinehurst
                  Resort Croquet Courts.  For more information call
                  (910) 295-8555 or (910) 295-6811.

   17 - 18        JOHN RUSH HUNTER JUMPER SHOW.  Hours:  8 AM. 
                  Pinehurst Track, Route 5.  For more information call
                  (910) 295-4446.

   17 - 18        GALLERIES OPEN.  Hours:  2-4 PM.  Campbell House,
                  Southern Pines.  For more information call
                  (910) 692-4356.

