<body background="./graphics/goldmrbl.jpg">
<img align=right src="./graphics/chamber1.gif">
<h3>The Sandhills Area Chamber of Commerce</h3>
<pre>

<a href="./members.html">Members</a>				<a href="./bizclass.html">Business</a>			<a href="whoswho.html">Who's Who</a></pre>
<hr>
<h3>Welcome!</h3>

<p>Welcome to Moore County! The high quality of life here makes us stand out as one of North Carolina's premier communities. We combine the warmth of a small town atmosphere with big city amenities few areas can claim.  

<p>Known as the Sandhills for our sandy soil and gentle rolling hills, we are blessed with a moderate climate that avails itself to year' round outdoor fun... and oh the fun we have!  We have wonderfully thrilling events such as steeplechases, tennis tournaments, polo, bicycle races and who could forget, golf!

<p>Where in the world can you imagine the top professional golfers on the planet coming to your backdoor, playing on your courses!?!?  It is here that they come!  For over a hundred years Pinehurst has been synonymous with golf. With 38 expertly designed and groomed courses in Moore County, we are unquestionably  "The Golf Capital of the World." Just think of the envy of those pros knowing that you can play these courses whenever you want....hey, you can even live on one!

<p>There is even more that our county offers you.  We have arts, history, botanical gardens, community festivals, unique shopping...There is something for everyone.  You came because you heard about our high quality of life. You'll stay because your quality of life in Moore County will be better than you heard. 


<pre>
<A HREF="./gro.html"><img align=bottom border=0 src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt=" * "> Growth & Development</A>			<A HREF="./his.html"><img align=bottom border=0 src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt=" * "> History</A>

