<HEAD><TITLE>Sandhills Libraries</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY background="./graphics/cloudy.gif"><H3>
<center><font size=+3>L</font>ibraries in the
<font size=+3>S</font>andhills</center></H3>
<P><HR><P>

<IMG ALT="books" width=199 height=44 ALIGN=right SRC="./graphics/books-2.gif"><A HREF="./lib-list.html">

<img align=bottom border=0 src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> Local Libraries and Information Centers</A><P><A HREF="./lib-link.html">
<img align=bottom border=0 src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> Links of Interest to Information Seekers</A>
<P><HR>

<P><font size=+3>T</font>here are a variety of library services available to residents of <a href="./county.html">Moore County</a>.

<P>Local public and community libraries lend <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/Web/booknew.html">books</a>, <a href="http://www.edoc.com/ejournal/magazines.html">magazines</a>, books-on-tape, and videos to card holders.

<P>They provide collections of reference sources such as
<a href="http://c.gp.cs.cmu.edu:5103/prog/webster">dictionaries</a>, 
so users can find the information they need.

<P><font size=+3>I</font>nformation-seekers can get reference assistance in locating the answers to such questions as "What is the 
<a href="http://www.census.gov/cgi-bin/popclock">current population</a> 
of the United States?"<P>Interesting 
<a href="http://ipl.sils.umich.edu/youth/StoryHour/">story and discussion programs</a> for children and adults are offered at most libraries.

<P>They provide inter-library loan services and share resources with other libraries around the 
<a href="http://hal.dcr.state.nc.us/ncslhome.htm">State</a>, 
the <a href="http://www.loc.gov/">Nation</a>, and the 
<a href="http://portico.bl.uk/">World</a>.

<P><font size=+3>T</font>he Katharine L. Boyd Library at 
<a href="http://www.sandhills.cc.nc.us/Sandhills/">Sandhills Community College</a> is one of North Carolina's many 
<a href="http://sunsite.unc.edu/reference/aal/">academic libraries</a>, providing specialized resources for students and teachers to support courses taught there.  Adult residents of Moore County may also obtain borrowing cards.

<P>In addition to serving the hospital staff, the 
<A HREF="./lib-list.html#hcic">Health Care Information Center</A> at Moore Regional Hospital provides the general public with information on community and personal health issues.

<P>Students and teachers in 
<a href="./sl_edu01.html">Moore County Schools</a> have access to information through school media centers.

<P><HR><P>Our <b>Libraries</b> page is sponsored by the <i><b>Southern Pines Public Library</b></i>.

<P>For more information about this site, or to suggest additional materials, please <A HREF="mailto:info@sandhills.net"><b>send us e-mail.</b></A>

