<h3><font size=+3>M</font>oore <font size=+3>C</font>ounty 
<font size=+3>G</font>overnment</h3>

<P><HR><P>

<IMG ALT="moore county" width=150 height=147 ALIGN=right  SRC="./graphics/mc-seal.gif">

<a href="http://www.webbuild.com/~vandy/"><img align=bottom border=0
src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> County of Moore WWW Site</a>
<p>

<A HREF="#mgr"><img align=bottom border=0
src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> County Manager</A><BR>
<A HREF="#commission"><img align=bottom border=0
src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> County Commissioners</A><BR>
<A HREF="#elect"><img align=bottom border=0
src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> Board of Elections</A><BR>
<A HREF="#court"><img align=bottom border=0
src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> Moore County Courthouse</A><BR>
<A HREF="#other"><img align=bottom border=0
src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt="*"> Other Offices</A><BR>

<P><HR><P>

<font size=+3>M</font>oore County is an exciting place to live and work! This site has
been established to provide information about the many activities
and services of the County of Moore.
<P>

<!--

NOTE--We don't have this yet:

You can see your County Commissioners and their contact
information or hear a message from the County Manager.

-->

<font size=+3>W</font>e want this to be an interactive and ever-changing site. To
accomplish this we need feedback from you. Please <a
href="mailto:info@sandhills.net">send us e-mail</a> to tell us what
information you would like to have provided here. Input from you
is what will make this service a success.
