<head>
<title>Sandhills.Net: The Chamber: Retirement Communities</title>
</head>

<body background="./graphics/goldmrbl.jpg">
<h3>Retirement Communities</h3>
<hr>
<p>If you are thinking of moving to Moore County and are looking for retirement living that offers you a strong sense of community with the opportunity for independent living, then you will find it here.  Moore County residents enjoy an active lifestyle at any age.  We have many  exclusive neighborhoods that are targeted for those over 50.  You can choose from single unit homes, patio homes, or townhouses.  There are even golf communities strictly for seniors.

<p>If you should desire a communal atmosphere combined with an independent active lifestyle, we have three facilities that offer individual apartments or townhouses that are fully staffed and offer ammenities such as laundry service, cleaning services, banks and transportation.  

<p>Whatever your desire for retirement living you will find an option here that will suit your wishes.

<hr>
see also: <A HREF="./sl_hea05.html"><img align=bottom border=0 src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt=" * "> Sandhills.Net: Life Care & Retirement Communities</A>
<center>
<A HREF="./index.html"><img align=bottom border=0 src="./graphics/bluebal2.gif" alt=" * "> The Sandhills Home Pages: Main</A>
</center>

</body>
