<head><title>SandLink: How To Find Us</title>
</head><body background="./graphics/prplmrbl.jpg"> 

<img align=right width=200 height=401 hspace=10 alt="Sandhills Map" 
src="./graphics/sh-map.jpg">

<h2>How To Find Us</h2>

<hr><p>

<font size=+1><b>By Auto . . .</b><p>

<blockquote>from Interstates 95, 85 and 40, with direct access by
U.S. 1, U.S. 15-501, N.C. 2, N.C. 5, & N.C. 211.</blockquote><p>

<b>By Air . . .</b><p>

<blockquote>using direct service by USAir Express via Charlotte
to the Moore County Airport (also handles private aircraft up to
BAC III) or other air service from Fayetteville, Greensboro and
Raleigh/Durham.</blockquote><p>

<b>By Train . . .</b><p>

<blockquote>via AMTRAK.</blockquote></font><p>

<P><hr>
 
For more information about this site, or to suggest additional materials,  
please <A HREF="mailto:info@sandhills.net"><b>send us e-mail.</b></A>
 
