<!--
Document Name: sl_ass.html
Author(s): Martin E. Locklear, Bob Howell
Copyright 1996 by the Sandhills Area Chamber of Commerce
                      1480 Hwy. 15-501		P.O. Box 458
		      Southern Pines, NC  28388
