<head>
<title>Sandhills.Net: Health: Hospital Services</title>
</head>

<body BACKGROUND="./graphics/m0oe9ihe.gif">
<!-- start body stuff here -->
<h2>Hospital Services</h2>

<p>Did you know the Sandhills has one of the most extensive medical communities providing comprehensive acute care services?

<p>With the need for specialized medical attention and emergency medical
services continually increasing, the Sandhills area is fortunate to have wide variety of hospital services available in several locations throughout the community.  Physicians and nursing staffs are prepared to handle almost any major medical concern from cardiovascular surgery to the delivery of babies.

<h5>Hospitals convenient to the Sandhills:</h5>
<ul>
<li>Montgomery Memorial Hospital, P.O. Box 486, Troy, NC, 27371, (910) 572-1301
<li>Moore Regional Hospital, P.O. Box 3000, Pinehurst, NC, 28374, (910) 215-1478
</ul>

