<head>
<title>Sandhills.Net: Health: Mental Health</title>
</head>

<body BACKGROUND="./graphics/m0oe9ihe.gif">
<!-- start body stuff here -->
<h2>Mental Health</h2>

<p>Did you know that comprehensive mental health services are available
through a variety of sources in the Sandhills?

<p>Residents of the Sandhills can seek counseling for such concerns as
depression, marital stress or substance abuse from any number of
clinics, centers and private practices. Professionals in the Sandhills are
experienced in dealing with myriad problems that can cause depression,
anxiety or other behavioral abnormalcies.

<h5>Mental Health Care Providers:</h5>
<ul>
<li><address><a href="http://www.ac.net/~twlane/CCLLC.html">Cardinal Clinic, LLC</a><br>
            351 Wagoner Drive, Suite 200, Fayetteville, NC 28303 
                voice (910) 867-8889, Fax: (910) 867-8999 <br>
            160-J Pinehurst Avenue, Southern Pines, NC 28387
                voice (910) 693-7777, Fax: (910) 693-1524</address>
<li>     Sandhills Center for Mental Health, PO Box 9, Seven Lakes, West End, NC 27376,  (910) 673-9111<br>
<li>     see phonebook for listing of Psychiatrists
</ul>


