<head>
<title>Sandhills.Net: Comm-Unity Links</title>
</head>

<body background="./graphics/pa01.jpg">

<h3>Comm-Unity Links</h3>
<hr>
<p>Links from this page fall in two categories; personal non-commercial pages and pages that SandLink has determined to have potential value to our community.  SandLink reserves the right to determine what links to provide and to discontinue links without notice.  

<p>If you have a link to suggest please <a href="mailto:link_request@sandhills.net">e-mail us your suggestion.</a>  Suggestions will be review as quickly as possible.  

<p>DISCLAIMER: This page is provided as part of the SandLink mission to provide a central access point for our community.  SandLink, The Sandhills Area Chamber of Commerce and the sponsoring organizations accept no responsibility for material beyond this page.
<br><br>
Our <b>Comm-Unity Links</b> page could be sponsored by <i><b>you or your company.</b></i>
<hr>

<a href="http://www.ac.net/">Alphanet - the host of <b>Sandhills.Net!</b></A><BR><BR>

<a href="http://www.webbuild.com/~wrhowell">Bob's Beta</a><br><br>

<a href="http://www.pinehurst.net">Internet of the Sandhills</a><br><br>

<a href="http://www.sandhills.org">Sandhills Electronic Magazine of Pinehurst, Southern Pines, NC</a><br><br>

<a href="http://www.sandhills.nc.us">Sandhills.NC.US including Pinehurst and Carthage North Carolina</a><br><br>

<a href="http://www.ac.net/locklem">Tampa Blue's Page</a><br><br>

<a href="http://ils.unc.edu/parkproject/wewo.html">Weymouth Woods - Sandhills Nature Preserve</a><br>

