<head>
<title>Sandhills.Net: Health: Internet Health Resources</title>
</head>
<body background="./graphics/m0oe9ihe.gif" bgcolor="00ffff">
<h3>Internet Health Resources</h3>
<hr>
<p>Here are some sources of health related information available on the 'Net.  We hope you find them useful.

<ul>
<h4>National</h4>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.ghsl.nwu.edu/healthweb/">HealthWeb</A>
<p>A project of the Committee on Institutional Cooperation member medical and health sciences libraries. Use this information server to find out about these libraries and their services, to connect to specialized health information resources developed at these universities, and retrieve other health related information.<br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.hcfa.gov">Health Care Financing Administration</A><br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.osha.gov">OSHA</A>
<p>The mission of the Occupational Safety and Health Administration (OSHA) is to save lives, prevent injuries and protect the health of America's workers.<br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.ageinfo.org">National Aging Information Center</A>
<p>The National Aging Information Center (NAIC), a service of the Administration on Aging (AoA), is the central source for a wide variety of program- and policy-related materials and demographic and other statistical data on the health, economic, and social status of older Americans. Established under the Older Americans Act, NAIC opened in September 1995. Most of NAIC's services are free of charge.<br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.ptct.com/html/industry.html">Home Care Industry Sites</A><br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://ube.ubalt.edu/www/bereavement/">Bereavement and Hospice Support Netline</A>
<p>We hope that this on-line directory of bereavement support groups and services and hospice bereavement programs from across the United States will provide you with information to help you or others you care about find appropriate help and support in coping with issues of loss and grief.
<br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.seniornet.com/">SeniorNet</A><br><br>

<li><p><a href="http://www.senior.com/aahsa">American Association of Homes and Services for the Aging</a>

<h4>North Carolina</h4>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www2.interpath.net/nchica/prospect.html">The North Carolina Health Care Information and Communications Alliance</A><br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.ehnr.state.nc.us/EHNR/SCHS/">North Carolina Public Health Home Page</A><br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://www.deh.ehnr.state.nc.us/">Welcome to DEH!</A> North Carolina's Department of Environmental Health<br><br>

<li><p><A HREF="http://moore.med.unc.edu/ocme/">Office of the Chief Medical Examiner</A><br>

</ul>
