<title>Sandhills.Net: Health: Dental, Vision & Chiropractic Services</title>
</head>

<body BACKGROUND="./graphics/m0oe9ihe.gif">
<!-- start body stuff here -->
<h2>Dental, Vision & Chiropractic Services</h2>

<p>Did you know that every form of dental and optical specialties can be 
found in the Sandhills?

<p>Although none of us necessarily enjoys extensive dental work, it is 
comforting to know that all of the major dental specialty services are 
available within a short drive from home.  Orthodontists, Periodontists and 
Prosthodontists all have offices in the heart of the Sandhills.  Likewise, 
optical care is available from multiple sources including private practices 
and clinics for medical and surgical eye care and popular retailers for 
lenses and frames.

<h5>Dental, Optical & Chiropractic Care Providers:</h5>
<ul>
<li>  Burley-Stroker Chiropractic, 1545 US1 South, Southern Pines, NC 28387, (910) 692-9006
<li>  Carolina Chiropractic Clinic, PA, 135 Turner Street, Yadkin Park, Southern Pines, NC  28387, (910) 692-2188
<li>  Seven Lakes Chiropractic Clinic, Seven Lakes Drive, West End, NC 27376, (910) 673-2225
<li>  Southern Pines Chiropractic, PA, 575 SE Broad Street, Southern Pines, NC 28387, (910) 692-5207
<li>  see phonebook listings
</ul>

