<body BACKGROUND="./graphics/m0oe9ihe.gif">
<!-- start body stuff here -->
<h2>Long-Term Care (Nursing Homes)</h2>

<p>Did you know that skilled nursing care is available within a short drive
of every community in the Sandhills?

<p>When the responsibilities of caring for ill and/or elderly relatives grow
beyond the capabilities of family, friends and home health care, thats
when long-term care facilities and nursing homes present a practical
alternative.  The Sandhills currently offers residents a good selection of
long-term care facilities that relieve immediate family from the
exhaustive task of caring for loved ones by providing compassionate and
comprehensive medical care.

<h5>Long-Term Care Providers:</h5>
<ul>
<li>     Autumn Care of Raeford
<li>     Highland House of Fayetteville, Inc.
<li>     Holland Family Care Home
<li>     <a href="http://www.manorcare.com">Manor Care Nursing & Rehabilitation Center</a>
<li>     Pinehurst Nursing Center
<li>     Pinelake Health Care
<li>     <a href="http://www.sjp.org">St. Joseph of the Pines Knollwood Campus</a>
<li>     <a href="http://www.sjp.org">St. Joseph of the Pines Health Center</a>
<li>     see phonebook for information
</ul>

