<h2>Life Care & Retirement Communities</h2>

<p>Did you know the Sandhills offer retirement possibilities from pure
leisure to accommodations for people with special medical needs?

<p>Some retirees may find themselves in the unfortunate situation of not
being able to care for themselves or their household needs.  Fortunately
for these people, the Sandhills offer retirement living opportunities
ranging from collective retirement communities to life care retirement
communities that provide varying levels of medical supervision and
health care in addition to assistance with everyday chores.

<h5>Life Care & Retirement Communities and Homes:</h5>
<ul>
<li>     see phonebook for listing of retirement communities & homes
</ul>
