http://aflcio.org:80/estatements/srawberr.htm 204.127.237.106 19970215053308 text/html 3458
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 05:33:02 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 14:41:29 GMT
Content-length: 3271
