http://aflcio.org:80/estatements/feb96/ecorg.html 204.127.237.106 19970215054534 text/html 8094
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Saturday, 15-Feb-97 05:45:20 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 22-Jan-97 14:40:29 GMT
